name: DUO protective sleeve for iPad / black
description:
DUO collection protective sleeve gives today's creative professional and fashion gadget lovers, a stylish options to protect their new gear safe from scratches + scuffs. 
"clutch-a-like style, compatible with both iPad & iPad2"

materials:
–premium washed faux-leather to assure perfect soft touch
–high density Tricot microfiber inner lining

features:
–durable form-fitted construction with weather resistant coating
–fully-lined microfiber inner fabric for ultimate preotection
-scratches free bumper closure
-external logo branding
-YKK heavy-duty zipper

official website: http://www.fantabulous.it/
